# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Social Content Engine — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this to .env and fill in your values

# ── General ──
APP_NAME=social-content-engine
DEBUG=true

# ── Database ──
DATABASE_URL=sqlite+aiosqlite:///./storage/social_engine.db

# ── Directus ──
DIRECTUS_URL=http://localhost:8055
DIRECTUS_ACCESS_TOKEN=
DIRECTUS_EMAIL=
DIRECTUS_PASSWORD=
DIRECTUS_SOURCES_COLLECTION=content_sources
DIRECTUS_IDEAS_COLLECTION=content_ideas
DIRECTUS_DRAFTS_COLLECTION=content_drafts
DIRECTUS_PUBLISH_TARGETS_COLLECTION=publish_targets
DIRECTUS_CAROUSEL_ASSETS_COLLECTION=carousel_assets
DIRECTUS_WORKFLOW_EVENTS_COLLECTION=workflow_events

# ── Qdrant ──
# Options: "local" (no Docker), "memory" (ephemeral), "server" (Docker/cloud)
QDRANT_MODE=local
QDRANT_LOCAL_PATH=./storage/qdrant_data
QDRANT_HOST=localhost
QDRANT_PORT=6333
QDRANT_COLLECTION=content_chunks

# ── Embedding ──
# Options: "local" (free sentence-transformers) or "openai" (paid)
EMBEDDING_PROVIDER=local
OPENAI_API_KEY=

# ── AI Generation ──
# Options: "groq" (free tier) or "anthropic" (paid)
GENERATION_PROVIDER=groq
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your-groq-api-key
GROQ_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-opus-4-6

# ── Image Generation (Gemini — optional, leave empty to skip) ──
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# ── LinkedIn OAuth2 ──
LINKEDIN_ACCESS_TOKEN=
LINKEDIN_PERSON_URN=urn:li:person:YOUR_PERSON_ID

# ── Twitter/X OAuth2 ──
X_API_KEY=
X_API_SECRET=
X_ACCESS_TOKEN=
X_ACCESS_TOKEN_SECRET=
X_BEARER_TOKEN=

# ── Postiz ──
POSTIZ_API_URL=https://api.postiz.com/public/v1
POSTIZ_API_KEY=
POSTIZ_LINKEDIN_INTEGRATION_ID=
POSTIZ_X_INTEGRATION_ID=
POSTIZ_DEFAULT_DELAY_MINUTES=60
POSTIZ_WEBHOOK_SECRET=

# ── Storage ──
STORAGE_DIR=./storage
IMAGES_DIR=./storage/images
